the aristocratic vampires and their onetime slaves, the Lycans. In the Dark 
Ages, a young Lycan named Lucian emerges as a powerful leader who rallies 
the werewolves to rise up against Viktor, the cruel vampire king who has 
enslaved them. Lucian is joined by his secret lover, Sonja, in his battle 
against the Vampire army and his struggle for Lycan freedom
